  (text "MCU (docs/09 s.3): ESP32-S3-WROOM-1-N8R2 (quad PSRAM keeps IO35-37). Straps\nIO3/IO45/IO46 untouched; IO0 boot + EN reset buttons per Espressif guideline.\nUSB-C: data only via TPD2E001 clamp; VBUS lands on a test-point net; CC 5.1K\npulldowns advertise UFP. SuperSpeed pins have no pads on the 16P receptacle." (at 25.4 27.94 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid eaaee50b-354f-4d57-9d52-409d198b125d))
